  {panel}

Stream colours could be defined in Classic plans so that you could visualise versions from multiple projects grouped together.

Add colour coding or CPR releases to quickly see how different projects overlap so that you can easily make changes.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Portfolio Server*. Using *JIRA Portfolio Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JPOCLOUD-1636].
